sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Python Script
    participant API as training-hub<br/>Public API
    participant Algo as Algorithm<br/>Instance
    participant TR as torchrun<br/>Distributed Launcher
    participant Backend as Backend<br/>Implementation
    participant Engine as Training Engine<br/>(ilab/mini-trainer/<br/>Unsloth/ART/verl)
    participant GPU as GPU Cluster<br/>NCCL/FSDP
    participant Disk as Filesystem<br/>Checkpoints

    Note over User, Disk: Flow 1: SFT / OSFT Training Pipeline

    User->>API: sft(model, data, ...) or osft(...)
    API->>Algo: AlgorithmRegistry.create_algorithm()
    Algo->>TR: get_torchrun_params()<br/>args > env > defaults
    TR->>Backend: torchrun subprocess<br/>TCP master_addr:master_port
    Backend->>Engine: execute_training()<br/>Python API call
    Engine->>GPU: Distributed training<br/>DDP/FSDP via NCCL
    GPU-->>Engine: Training iterations
    Engine->>Disk: Save checkpoints
    Engine-->>Backend: Training complete
    Backend-->>Algo: Results
    Algo-->>User: Output path + metrics

    Note over User, Disk: Flow 2: LoRA+GRPO Training Pipeline (verl)

    User->>API: lora_grpo(model, data, reward_fn, ...)
    API->>Algo: AlgorithmRegistry.create_algorithm()
    Algo->>Backend: VeRLLoRAGRPOBackend
    Backend->>Disk: Write Parquet data
    Backend->>Disk: Write reward function file
    Backend->>Disk: Write YAML config
    Backend->>Engine: subprocess: verl.trainer.main_ppo
    Engine->>GPU: FSDP training loop

    Note right of Engine: vLLM inference server<br/>started as subprocess<br/>for rollout generation

    Engine->>GPU: Generate rollouts (vLLM)
    GPU-->>Engine: Rollout results
    Engine->>GPU: Policy gradient update
    GPU-->>Engine: Updated weights
    Engine->>Disk: Save checkpoints
    Backend->>Disk: Normalize checkpoint format
    Backend-->>User: Output path + metrics

    Note over User, Disk: Flow 3: GPU Memory Estimation

    User->>API: estimate(model, algorithm, ...)
    API->>Algo: Select estimator<br/>(Basic/OSFT/LoRA/QLoRA)
    Algo->>Engine: HuggingFace model config<br/>HTTPS/443 (TLS)
    Engine-->>Algo: Parameter count, architecture
    Algo->>Algo: Calculate memory requirements<br/>(weights + gradients + optimizer +<br/>activations + overhead)
    Algo-->>User: Memory estimate (GB)<br/>+ fit/no-fit per GPU
